==Add LV on existing VG==

(e.g., at ite-beta2)

  vgdisplay

must reveal empty space (Free PE / Size) on the volume group. 

Create new volume:

  lvcreate -v -L 200G -n "srv" vg00

Create file system:

  mkfs.ext4 /dev/vg00/srv

Add fstab entry:

  /dev/vg00/srv   /srv            ext4     defaults        0 2

==Rename LV==

  lvrename /dev/vg00/srv opt


